attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a table. He starts by unscrewing the first leg. After unscrewing the first leg he continues to do the same with the second, and third legs. Halfway by unscrewing the fourth leg, the student removes the shelf. Once the student unscrews all the hex sockets from the fourth leg, he detaches the top part from the table.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrew the first leg.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the hex socket head.
The student drops the allen wrench.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrew the second leg.
The student unscrew the third leg.
The student unscrew the fourth leg.
